    <p>{`As for the inbound and outbound rules, we add an inbound SSH rule for TCP, port 22, Anywhere which will allow in SSH connections.`}</p>
    <p>{`As a second option, we choose HTTPS and a HTTP role as well.`}</p>
    <p>{`For the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Outbound`}</inlineCode>{`, we want SSH to anywhere and HTTP and HTTPS as well. After configuring our services, we may want to choose a more restricive kind of traffic.`}</p>
    <p>{`Again, from here, we can edit the inbound and outbound rules too.`}</p>
    <p>{`We recommend that you only open up SSH to a few IP ranges.`}</p>
