    <p>{`These containers also run in a cluster. We can choose what instance type we want, and a number of instances.`}</p>
    <p>{`Key-Pairs are also region specific and you'll need a new key-pair for another cluster in a different region.`}</p>
    <p>{`We need to make sure `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`ecsinstanceRole`}</inlineCode>{` IAM policy is also currently allowed.`}</p>
