    <p>{`Head back to `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`ECS`}</inlineCode>{` and we can see in the clusters that we only have one running task.`}</p>
    <p>{`Now, if we select `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Clusters > Task`}</inlineCode>{`, we run a new task and choose our task definition. We still only need to run 1 task, since we just ran 1 additional instance. It's a 1-to-1 relationship.`}</p>
    <p>{`Something that is cool, is that just because we are running a new task, we don't have to choose the same definition eg. like how we are running a database to support the cluster.`}</p>
